    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>晚上花了几个小时，趟了好多坑，不过顺利的建立起人生的第一个博客还是很开心的</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="course"><a href="#course" class="headerlink" title="course:"></a>course:</h2><p>1.<a href="https://www.simon96.online/2018/10/12/hexo-tutorial/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">最全Hexo博客搭建+主题优化+插件配置+常用操作+错误分析</a><br>同时这也算是一个优秀博客网站的示例。<br>2.<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo框架官方文档</a><br>3.<a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">next主题官方文档</a><br>4.<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/e8e5addbbcfd" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo+Next配置Blog</a><br>5.<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/f054333ac9e6?utm_campaign=maleskine&utm_content=note&utm_medium=seo_notes&utm_source=recommendation" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo的next主题个性化教程：打造炫酷网站</a><br>6.<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/lemonxq/article/details/72676005" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo静态博客搭建+个人定制</a><br>7.<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/e8e5addbbcfd" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo+Next配置Blog</a><br>8.<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/9f0e90cc32c2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo-NexT配置超炫网页效果</a><br>9.<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/superjimmy/article/details/51626842" target="_blank" rel="noopener">手把手教你用github pages搭建博客 最新版</a><br>10.<a href="https://pages.github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github pages官方文档如何让搭建网站(非常实用，不限制于博客引擎)</a><br>11.<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/u011475210/article/details/79023429" target="_blank" rel="noopener">我的个人博客之旅：从jekyll到hexo</a></p><h2 id="html-commands-reference"><a href="#html-commands-reference" class="headerlink" title="html commands reference:"></a>html commands reference:</h2><p>1.<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/nanjinzhu/article/details/82734528" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HTML特效代码大全(完整)</a><br>2.<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/alashan007/article/details/78215224" target="_blank" rel="noopener">网页html代码大全</a></p><h2 id="javascript-learning"><a href="#javascript-learning" class="headerlink" title="javascript learning:"></a>javascript learning:</h2><p>1.<a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/js/index.asp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">JavaScript 教程(w3school)</a><br>2.<a href="https://www.runoob.com/js/js-tutorial.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">JavaScript 教程(runoob.com)</a></p><h2 id="good-example"><a href="#good-example" class="headerlink" title="good example:"></a>good example:</h2><p>1.<a href="https://www.simon96.online/2018/10/12/hexo-tutorial/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">遇见西门</a><br>2.<a href="https://weisongzhao.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">weisong</a><br>3.<a href="https://crayonnew.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nino’s blog</a></p><h2 id="book"><a href="#book" class="headerlink" title="book"></a>book</h2><p><a href="http://iissnan.com/progit/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">pro git书</a><br><a href="https://www.bootcss.com/p/git-guide/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">git教学极简版本</a></p><h2 id="commands"><a href="#commands" class="headerlink" title="commands:"></a>commands:</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"我个人博客的第一篇博客，哈哈哈..."</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo s --debug   //调试网页</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo clean  //清理缓存</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g    //重新生成博客代码</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo d   //部署到远端(github)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
